==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Damson
<hw>Dam"son</hw> <pr>(d⟦acr⟧m"z'n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>damasin</ets> the Damascus plum, fr. L. Damascenus. See
<er>Damascene</er>.]</ety> <def>A small oval plum of a blue color, the
fruit of a variety of the <spn>Prunus domestica</spn>; -- called also
<altname>damask plum</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dan</ent>⟦br⟧
